<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2011/index.html">SLE 2011</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2011/paper17.html">RLSRunner: Linking Rascal with K for Program Analysis</a></em> (<a href="../profile/MarkHills.html">Mark Hills</a>, <a href="../profile/PaulKlint.html">Paul Klint</a>, <a href="../profile/JurgenVinju.html"><span class="info">Jurgen Vinju</span></a>) </li>
